snippet.title: VTOL VR - Trailer (2020)
snippet.description:
Game: VTOL VR - Full Release now available on Steam
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/667970/VTOL_VR/
Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/vtol-vr
Website: https://vtolvr.bdynamicsstudio.com/

VTOL VR is a near-futuristic combat flight game built for Virtual Reality. Pilot advanced multi-role jets, using your hands to flip switches, press buttons, and manipulate the virtual flight controls.
Enjoy!
